Required packeages
 -Node.js (http://nodejs.org)
 -Node Package Manager (http://npmjs.org)
 -Redis (http://redis.io)

Install Node.js 
 -wget http://nodejs.org/dist/node-v0.4.8.tar.gz
 -tar xzf node-v0.4.8.tar.gz
 -cd node-v0.4.8
 -./configure  
 -make
 -sudo make install

Install Node Package Manager (npm)
 -curl http://npmjs.org/install.sh | sudo sh  

Install Redis
 -wget http://redis.googlecode.com/files/redis-2.2.7.tar.gz
 -tar xzf redis-2.2.7.tar.gz 
 -cd redis-2.2.7  
 -make
 -cd src
 -make
 -sudo make install
 
Install SocketStream
 -git clone git://github.com/socketstream/socketstream.git
 -cd socketstream/
 -npm install -g
 
Start redis server
 -redis-server

Start app
 -socketstream start
